+# Phase 4: GlobalState Re-enablement — Task Dossier
+
+**Plan**: [sse-multiplexing-plan.md](../../sse-multiplexing-plan.md)
+**Phase**: Phase 4: GlobalState Re-enablement
+**Generated**: 2026-03-08
+**Domain**: `_platform/state`
